    </node>
    <node id="NOPARALLEL">
      <data key="d0">NOPARALLEL</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">NOPARALLEL is a database index option and property, primarily used in Oracle databases, that specifies index creation and maintenance are performed serially, using a single process or thread rather than in parallel. By disabling parallel execution for index operations, NOPARALLEL ensures that these tasks are not distributed across multiple processes, which can impact the speed and performance of index creation and maintenance. This setting is often chosen for smaller tables, when system resources are limited, or when it is necessary to avoid resource contention and parallelism offers no significant benefit. NOPARALLEL is used to ensure predictable and controlled resource usage during index operations, such as for specific indexes like LOC_STATE_PROVINCE_IX, by preventing parallel execution and thereby managing how resources are allocated during index maintenance. Overall, NOPARALLEL favors simplicity and predictability over potential speed gains from parallel execution, making it suitable for environments where controlled resource usage and avoidance of contention are priorities.&lt;SEP&gt;NOPARALLEL is a database setting that disables parallel execution for index operations, affecting performance and resource usage during index creation or rebuilds.&lt;SEP&gt;NOPARALLEL is an index property indicating that index operations are performed serially, potentially to avoid resource contention or because the table size does not warrant parallel processing.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-ac0843275fead0fc502c43470c04f3a2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1de866b5986aebcccae444bb76f0105b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-51ba69f951ee5b889d1443142c78204b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bb684b9b744514893d0d1b99289bbe05&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf21f34bdc08f5a0331c894d66d1eb31&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-60fc3f432e526e12067b6a12ccbff962&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0ca92db0127a6ddd811d5e51df59e9bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7caa66c20d092a335dc8648173fb5354&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9fedc09939f22511bb84ca5aa5751c23&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a41048dcaa5356d2ec9a434224117f92&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-410ac6b3623a033ae62dfa51c383d7a0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f5b845ca1a4e306071c9c2fa3b01b60&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e24ec303a0c36890649afea58f3fecf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f93583342dc27c6c3331c90c22264c1b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b4c65c6163252963d56c1f1400c52aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bcb6882954ebc0bf73a53009f4e43c91&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-db329f300a48c02eb5236b03367fb951</data>
