    <node id="EMPLOYEES Table">
      <data key="d0">EMPLOYEES Table</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">A likely dependent table in the HR schema that may reference the HR.COUNTRIES table for country information, supporting employee data management.&lt;SEP&gt;The EMPLOYEES table is a table within the HR schema that likely references the LOCATIONS table to associate employees with specific physical locations.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-e34db40cf2365e32f299f601d34d886a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d57c05e29cac79ec75bdc43f56c5d29</data>
