      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">Business Reporting refers to the generation of reports based on city data, which is made more efficient by the LOC_CITY_IX index.&lt;SEP&gt;Business Reporting refers to the generation of reports for business analysis, using data from HR.JOB_HISTORY and indexes.&lt;SEP&gt;Business reporting involves generating reports and analytics, often segmented by country, which benefit from the optimized access provided by LOC_COUNTRY_IX.</data>
