      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">Storage Usage refers to the amount of database storage consumed by the LOC_CITY_IX index, which can be affected by options like NOCOMPRESS.&lt;SEP&gt;Storage Usage refers to the amount of disk space consumed by the index, affected by properties like NOCOMPRESS.</data>
