      <data key="d0">Resource Contention</data>
      <data key="d1">event</data>
      <data key="d2">Resource Contention refers to competition for database resources, which can be minimized by using the NOPARALLEL option during index creation and maintenance.&lt;SEP&gt;Resource Contention refers to competition for system resources during index operations, which NOPARALLEL may help to avoid.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-7b4c65c6163252963d56c1f1400c52aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-60fc3f432e526e12067b6a12ccbff962</data>
