    <node id="JHIST_DATE_INTERVAL constraint">
      <data key="d0">JHIST_DATE_INTERVAL constraint</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">JHIST_DATE_INTERVAL constraint is a business rule that enforces END_DATE to be greater than START_DATE in JOB_HISTORY.</data>
