      <data key="d0">Job Assignment</data>
      <data key="d1">event</data>
      <data key="d2">Job Assignment refers to the period during which an employee holds a specific job role in a department, as recorded in JOB_HISTORY.&lt;SEP&gt;Job assignment is the business process of assigning a job role to an employee, typically during onboarding or role changes, using the HR.JOBS table as the reference for valid job titles.</data>
