      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">hr.EMP_DETAILS_VIEW is a database view in the HR schema that centralizes employee, job, department, and geographic data for comprehensive HR reporting and analysis. It is read-only, enforces data integrity, and is used in various business processes and analytics.&lt;SEP&gt;hr.EMP_DETAILS_VIEW is a read-only database view in the HR schema, designed to provide a comprehensive, denormalized snapshot of employee details by joining multiple related tables. It consolidates employee, job, department, location, country, and region information into a single, easily queryable structure for business users, analysts, and applications requiring holistic employee data.</data>
