      <data key="d0">HR.LOCATIONS</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">HR.LOCATIONS is a database table in the HR schema that stores information about physical locations used by the organization. It is referenced by the HR.DEPARTMENTS table to associate departments with locations.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-2062c94493f296606e14ada3763e1f63</data>
