    <node id="DEPARTMENT_NAME">
      <data key="d0">DEPARTMENT_NAME</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">DEPARTMENT_NAME is a mandatory attribute representing the name of each department, required for data completeness and integrity.&lt;SEP&gt;The human-readable name of a department, such as Administration, Marketing, etc. It is a required field in HR.DEPARTMENTS and supports up to 30 characters.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-2062c94493f296606e14ada3763e1f63&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a837c6cab856c3245b8657e36779634a</data>
