      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">Factors affecting the operation of the HR.DEPARTMENTS table, such as the impact of changes to referenced tables and backup strategies.&lt;SEP&gt;Operational Considerations are factors such as index fragmentation, bloat, and the need for compression or parallelism, which affect ongoing index performance.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-5e24ec303a0c36890649afea58f3fecf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a837c6cab856c3245b8657e36779634a</data>
