      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">A set of rules and constraints that govern the structure, integrity, and operation of the HR.DEPARTMENTS table.&lt;SEP&gt;Comprehensive Constraints &amp; Rules are the set of requirements and limitations governing the use of the index and JOB_HISTORY table.</data>
