    <node id="redo log">
      <data key="d0">redo log</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">The redo log is a database component in Oracle that records changes for recovery purposes. The NOLOGGING option for DEPT_LOCATION_IX reduces redo log usage.</data>
