      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">Management Reporting encompasses the processes and tools used to generate reports and analyses about the management structure, employee reporting lines, and organizational charts, often relying on efficient access to manager-employee relationships.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-410ac6b3623a033ae62dfa51c383d7a0</data>
      <data key="d4">hr.emp_manager_ix.md</data>
      <data key="d5">1753988357</data>
