      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">Backup and Recovery Planning involves strategies to ensure data integrity and recoverability, especially important when using NOLOGGING indexes.&lt;SEP&gt;Backup and Recovery Planning refers to the strategies and processes for ensuring data integrity and availability in the event of data loss or system failure. NOLOGGING indexes require special consideration in this context.</data>
