      <data key="d1">event</data>
      <data key="d2">Index creation and maintenance operations are database events involving the building or updating of indexes, such as EMP_DEPARTMENT_IX, with options like NOLOGGING, NOCOMPRESS, and NOPARALLEL affecting their behavior.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-a01dcf1c9756eb26a45470d65ee6f338</data>
      <data key="d4">hr.emp_department_ix.md</data>
      <data key="d5">1753988669</data>
