    <node id="Business Processes Relying on Department-Level Employee Data Segmentation">
      <data key="d0">Business Processes Relying on Department-Level Employee Data Segmentation</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">These are organizational workflows and activities that depend on efficiently accessing and managing employee data segmented by department, supported by the EMP_DEPARTMENT_IX index.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-a41048dcaa5356d2ec9a434224117f92</data>
