      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">MIN_SALARY is a column in the HR.JOBS table indicating the minimum salary allowed for a job title. It is optional and used in compensation validation and salary band enforcement.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-35af4e5a5e00230258378b2941dcb564</data>
      <data key="d4">hr.jobs.md</data>
