      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">Job roles refer to the various positions or titles defined within the HR.JOBS table, each associated with specific salary ranges and business rules.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-2e8912ac03211e6d10a671c1a31ccb8e</data>
      <data key="d4">hr.jobs.md</data>
