    <edge source="NOLOGGING" target="Index Creation">
      <data key="d6">23.0</data>
      <data key="d7">NOLOGGING affects the index creation process by minimizing redo log generation.&lt;SEP&gt;NOLOGGING is used during index creation to reduce redo log generation and speed up the process.&lt;SEP&gt;NOLOGGING is an option used during index creation to minimize redo log generation.</data>
