      <data key="d7">The LOC_STATE_PROVINCE_IX index uses the NOLOGGING setting to reduce redo log usage during index operations, impacting performance and recoverability.&lt;SEP&gt;The index is created with the NOLOGGING property, reducing redo log generation during index operations for performance reasons.</data>
      <data key="d8">index property,logging,performance tuning</data>
      <data key="d9">chunk-51ba69f951ee5b889d1443142c78204b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9fedc09939f22511bb84ca5aa5751c23</data>
